\sin \theta = \frac{2}{\pi}-\frac{4}{\pi}\sum_1^{\infty}\frac{\cos 2n\theta}{4n^2-1}\;\;\;\;(0\leq\theta\leq \pi)\;\;\;\;(*),
\cos\theta=\frac{d}{d\theta}\sin\theta = -\int_{\pi/2}^\theta \sin\phi \:d\phi.
